WEBVTT

00:03.012 --> 00:04.812
<i>Previously on</i> Damages...

00:04.814 --> 00:06.580
McCLAREN: I didn't
know Naomi Walling.

00:06.782 --> 00:09.116
She contacted my organization
as a whistleblower.

00:09.118 --> 00:13.420
I don't know how her personal
correspondence made its way into the leak.

00:13.422 --> 00:14.421
Every life lost is a tragedy.

00:14.423 --> 00:16.723
PARSONS: Ms. Hewes cannot
prove that my client had any

00:16.725 --> 00:19.059
reasons to expose
Ms. Walling's personal life.

00:19.061 --> 00:22.930
HEWES: I filed a wrongful death
suit against Mr. McClaren.

00:22.932 --> 00:25.532
The first thing that we're gonna
need to do is find out if your

00:25.534 --> 00:28.702
mother had a personal
relationship with Mr. McClaren.

00:28.704 --> 00:32.171
SIMON: This scandal has given
many of our donors pause.

00:32.174 --> 00:33.173
We have a cash flow problem.

00:33.175 --> 00:35.175
HEWES: So you're
looking for a job.

00:35.177 --> 00:38.178
FRANKLIN: Actually, an old friend of
yours has already offered me one.

00:38.180 --> 00:40.180
So how about you double
the girl's offer?

00:40.182 --> 00:43.283
I figure that's a fair price to
keep someone from your past from

00:43.285 --> 00:44.585
working for the other side.

00:44.587 --> 00:46.220
She offered me a job.

00:46.222 --> 00:48.755
You were right, she does not
want me to work for you.

00:48.757 --> 00:49.656
PARSONS: Naomi Walling.

00:49.658 --> 00:52.326
She rented a room the night
before the leak went public.

00:52.328 --> 00:53.160
That's him.

00:53.162 --> 00:54.862
PARSONS: - Who?
- McClaren.

00:54.864 --> 00:56.964
He definitely met with
Walling before she died.

00:56.966 --> 00:58.198
Told you he was interesting.

00:58.200 --> 01:00.267
PARSONS: He's also a liar.

